text: Adolfo Rodríguez Saá (born 25 July 1947) is an Argentine Peronist politician. He was an interim President of Argentina between 23 December 2001 through 30 December 2001. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Argentina Category:Argentine lawyers Category:Peronists
title: Adolfo Rodríguez Saá
